HEADWORD: Brushing
<hw>Brush"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Constructed or used
to brush with; as a <xex>brushing</xex> machine.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Brisk; light; <as>as, a <ex>brushing</ex>
gallop</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Brushite</ent>⟦br⟧
